---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About" description="Learn about F3 - Fitness, Fellowship, Faith. A free workout movement for men.">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold mb-8">About F3</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-6">
          F3 is a national network of free, peer-led workouts for men. Our mission is to plant,
          grow, and serve small workout groups for men for the invigoration of male community leadership.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold mt-12 mb-4 text-white">The Three F's</h2>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-f3-red">Fitness</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">
              Our workouts are challenging, outdoor, and peer-led. No certifications required—just men
              pushing other men to be better. We believe in functional fitness that prepares you for
              the demands of daily life.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-f3-red">Fellowship</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">
              The bonds formed through shared suffering are unlike any other. F3 creates authentic
              relationships between men who might never have met otherwise. We do life together—beyond
              just the workout.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-f3-red">Faith</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">
              F3 is not a religious organization, but we believe in something bigger than ourselves.
              We encourage men to lead in their families, communities, and workplaces. We develop
              High Impact Men (HIM) who make a difference.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold mt-12 mb-4 text-white">Five Core Principles</h2>

        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-3 text-gray-400">
          <li><strong class="text-white">Free of charge</strong> — All F3 workouts are free, always.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Open to all men</strong> — Any man can join, regardless of fitness level.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Held outdoors</strong> — Rain or shine, we're outside.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Peer-led</strong> — Rotating leadership, no paid instructors.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">End with a Circle of Trust</strong> — We close together, sharing announcements and support.</li>
        </ol>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold mt-12 mb-4 text-white">Ready to Join?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          There's no signup, no registration, no fees. Just show up at any workout on our schedule.
          Look for the group of men, introduce yourself, and join in. We'll take care of the rest.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <a
          href="/workouts"
          class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-f3-red text-white font-display font-semibold text-lg rounded hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors"
        >
          Find a Workout Near You
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
